0:39:22.920 --> 0:39:24.922
My parents are dead.

0:39:25.053 --> 0:39:26.533
Oh.

0:39:26.663 --> 0:39:28.143
My brother...

0:39:34.105 --> 0:39:36.804
My brother is dead.

0:39:36.934 --> 0:39:38.849
I, uh...

0:39:42.549 --> 0:39:45.639
I got no wife...

0:39:45.769 --> 0:39:47.554
No kids.

0:39:47.684 --> 0:39:49.817
No friends.

0:39:49.947 --> 0:39:52.820
If I died tonight...

0:39:52.950 --> 0:39:55.213
no one would care.

0:39:55.344 --> 0:39:56.824
What difference would it make?

0:39:56.954 --> 0:39:59.043
Gene, buddy...

0:39:59.174 --> 0:40:04.222
No, I-I-I'm sure that you mean
a lot to, you know...

0:40:04.353 --> 0:40:05.876
To a lot of... lots of people.

0:40:06.007 --> 0:40:11.055
If I died tonight, my landlord
would pack up my stuff.

0:40:11.186 --> 0:40:14.319
It'd take him three hours.

0:40:14.450 --> 0:40:18.454
And Cinnabon would just
hire a new manager.

0:40:18.585 --> 0:40:19.716
Gene who?

0:40:19.847 --> 0:40:21.022
Poof!

0:40:21.152 --> 0:40:24.547
I'd be gone.
I'd be...

0:40:24.678 --> 0:40:26.810
a...

0:40:26.941 --> 0:40:28.725
a ghost.

0:40:28.856 --> 0:40:33.991
Less than a ghost.
I'd be a... a sha... shadow.

0:40:36.341 --> 0:40:38.256
I'd just be...

0:40:38.387 --> 0:40:39.997
nothing.

0:40:44.219 --> 0:40:48.136
I mean, Frank...
What's the point, Frank?

0:40:54.011 --> 0:40:55.970
What's the poi...

0:41:11.202 --> 0:41:14.118
Ah.

0:41:14.249 --> 0:41:16.381
Oh, you... I'm so sorry.

0:41:16.512 --> 0:41:17.948
You didn't need to hear
any of that.

0:41:18.079 --> 0:41:20.168
No, no, no, no, no,
that's... that's okay.

0:41:20.298 --> 0:41:21.909
No, that... that is okay.

0:41:24.128 --> 0:41:26.043
Everybody has bad days.

0:41:26.174 --> 0:41:27.741
You've felt like this?

0:41:30.265 --> 0:41:33.964
No, I mean, not me...
But people.

0:41:34.095 --> 0:41:35.792
I-I think a lot of people.

0:41:35.923 --> 0:41:39.709
Yeah, I mean, i-it's just like
life's ups and life's downs.

0:41:39.840 --> 0:41:42.538
Yeah.

0:41:42.669 --> 0:41:44.453
Hey, you're not gonna tell
Nick, are you?

0:41:44.584 --> 0:41:45.933
Oh.

0:41:46.063 --> 0:41:48.413
No, 'course not.

0:41:48.544 --> 0:41:50.981
Well... thanks so much
for listening.

0:41:51.112 --> 0:41:53.636
Yeah, no, no.
No p... No problem.

0:43:20.941 --> 0:43:22.072
I don't know.

0:43:22.203 --> 0:43:24.553
I'm thinking maybe
blue or black?

0:43:24.684 --> 0:43:25.859
What's the occasion?

0:43:25.989 --> 0:43:26.989
My sister's wedding.

0:43:27.034 --> 0:43:28.601
Oh, very exciting.

0:43:28.731 --> 0:43:30.167
Um, what size are you?

0:43:30.298 --> 0:43:32.082
Usually a 38 or a 40?

0:43:32.213 --> 0:43:33.431
Do you want to try both?

0:43:33.562 --> 0:43:34.781
Yeah.
Let's do it.

0:43:37.174 --> 0:43:39.873
Sir, do you need help?

0:43:40.003 --> 0:43:41.483
I'm good.

0:43:41.614 --> 0:43:43.877
Well, Barbara's right here
if you need anything.

0:43:44.007 --> 0:43:45.226
Mm-hmm.

0:43:45.356 --> 0:43:47.707
Kathy, is this it? Yes.

0:43:47.837 --> 0:43:50.884
Excuse me, ma'am? Truck's here
to pick up that big box.

0:43:51.014 --> 0:43:52.276
Great, thank you.

0:43:52.407 --> 0:43:54.496
Uh...
the guy brought flowers?

0:43:54.627 --> 0:43:56.150
Really?

0:44:25.832 --> 0:44:28.878
Look. Ooh la la! Ooh la la!

0:44:31.228 --> 0:44:32.839
Oh.
Check this out.

0:44:32.882 --> 0:44:34.623
Buongiorno, ladies!

0:44:34.754 --> 0:44:35.905
How much you think
we can get for 'em?

0:44:35.929 --> 0:44:37.529
I don't know.
Maybe... five hundred each?

0:44:37.626 --> 0:44:38.671
But shit, man.

0:44:38.801 --> 0:44:40.368
Maybe I just keep 'em
for myself.

0:44:40.498 --> 0:44:41.891
I've been eyeing these Jordans.

0:44:42.022 --> 0:44:45.547
You guys enjoying yourselves?

0:44:45.678 --> 0:44:46.838
Well, hold onto that feeling.

0:44:46.896 --> 0:44:48.419
'Cause this is it.

0:44:48.550 --> 0:44:49.551
Yeah, we know.

0:44:49.682 --> 0:44:51.292
Well, in case you forget...

0:44:51.422 --> 0:44:52.772
You transported stolen goods

0:44:52.902 --> 0:44:54.817
with a value exceeding
five thousand dollars.

0:44:54.948 --> 0:44:57.559
And the truck you used to do it
was rented in Council Bluffs,

0:44:57.690 --> 0:44:58.952
across state lines.

0:44:59.082 --> 0:45:01.389
You told us to rent
the truck over there...

0:45:01.519 --> 0:45:03.043
Theft from
an Interstate Shipment.

0:45:03.173 --> 0:45:04.740
Up to ten years.

0:45:04.871 --> 0:45:06.831
Transportation of Stolen Goods.
Another ten years.

0:45:06.873 --> 0:45:08.788
Sale of Stolen Goods.
Ten years.

0:45:08.918 --> 0:45:10.659
Conspiracy to commit
a federal crime...

0:45:10.790 --> 0:45:13.793
Whoa, whoa. "Conspiracy"?
It was your idea.

0:45:13.923 --> 0:45:16.709
Yeah. It's called
"mutually assured destruction."

0:45:16.839 --> 0:45:20.974
So, if I go down, you go down.

0:45:21.104 --> 0:45:22.299
Man, you don't
havta threaten us.

0:45:22.323 --> 0:45:23.716
We're all friends here.

0:45:26.631 --> 0:45:29.330
I am not your friend.

0:45:29.460 --> 0:45:30.940
And if you get greedy
and you decide

0:45:31.071 --> 0:45:33.900
to come back for more, don't.

0:45:34.030 --> 0:45:35.771
Gene Takavic...
You never heard of him.

0:45:35.902 --> 0:45:38.339
The Cottonwood Mall?
You don't go there.

0:45:38.469 --> 0:45:42.778
You see me coming, you cross
to the other side of the street.

0:45:42.909 --> 0:45:44.388
Dude...

0:45:44.519 --> 0:45:47.565
Now I need you to say it:
"we're done."

0:45:49.611 --> 0:45:51.526
Come on! Say it.

0:45:51.656 --> 0:45:53.963
"We're. Done."

0:45:54.094 --> 0:45:55.530
Say it.

0:46:05.279 --> 0:46:08.238
We're done.

0:46:08.369 --> 0:46:11.154
We're... We're done.

0:46:11.285 --> 0:46:12.721
Gene?

0:46:16.159 --> 0:46:18.335
Hey, Gene, I see your car!

0:46:22.731 --> 0:46:24.472
Gene?

0:46:35.918 --> 0:46:37.833
Well, that's a start.

0:46:37.964 --> 0:46:40.662
Looks like your problem
is the master cylinder.

0:46:40.793 --> 0:46:44.013
Look at you boys, hard at work.

0:46:44.144 --> 0:46:47.843
Well, Marion, guys,
I got to get going.

0:46:47.974 --> 0:46:50.150
I will take another look
next time.

0:46:50.280 --> 0:46:51.847
Wait a minute.

0:46:51.978 --> 0:46:53.607
No, you can't go anywhere
looking like that.

0:46:53.631 --> 0:46:56.025
Come on inside and wash up.

0:46:56.156 --> 0:46:58.071
Ma...

0:46:58.201 --> 0:47:00.638
Jeffie, don't vex me.
Come on, Gene.

0:47:00.769 --> 0:47:01.877
You can help me
with the groceries.

0:47:01.901 --> 0:47:04.599
Huh, Gene? Sounds like a plan.

0:47:16.219 --> 0:47:18.395
Nice of you to
help Jeffie with his car.

0:47:20.223 --> 0:47:23.748
You might not know it, but
my boy's had some tough times.

0:47:23.879 --> 0:47:28.666
He, uh... He fell in with
a bad crowd back in Albuquerque.

0:47:28.797 --> 0:47:32.105
Albuquerque, huh?
Never been.

0:47:32.235 --> 0:47:34.063
Lucky you.

0:47:34.194 --> 0:47:36.892
But things are so much better
for Jeffie here.

0:47:37.023 --> 0:47:40.156
Even more so
now that he knows you.

0:47:40.287 --> 0:47:43.507
You're a good influence, Gene.

0:47:43.638 --> 0:47:44.726
Oh, where's my brain?

0:47:44.857 --> 0:47:48.121
I keep forgetting to ask you
about Nippy.

0:47:49.600 --> 0:47:50.645
Nippy?

0:47:50.775 --> 0:47:53.648
Oh, oh, right.

0:47:53.778 --> 0:47:54.605
You're not gonna believe this,

0:47:54.736 --> 0:47:56.956
but, uh, he was with a family

0:47:57.086 --> 0:47:59.045
the whole time, just...
Just a few blocks away.

0:47:59.175 --> 0:48:00.481
Oh, well, that's wonderful!

0:48:00.611 --> 0:48:02.265
Yeah.
He's in great shape.

0:48:02.396 --> 0:48:06.095
So, after all that...

0:48:06.226 --> 0:48:08.097
a happy ending.

0:48:08.228 --> 0:48:09.751
Oh, well...

0:48:20.414 --> 0:48:22.503
Here you go, Ma'am.
Thanks.

0:48:22.633 --> 0:48:24.548
And looky here.

0:48:27.900 --> 0:48:30.250
For you, m'lady. Thank you.

0:48:33.514 --> 0:48:36.125
Hey, Gene,
aren't you taking lunch?

0:48:36.256 --> 0:48:37.866
Huh?

0:48:40.477 --> 0:48:42.175
Thanks.

0:50:43.252 --> 0:50:47.430
I get it.
You get over it, okay?

0:50:47.561 --> 0:50:49.258
Please, believe me.

0:50:49.389 --> 0:50:52.740
Before you know it,
you'll forget all about it.

0:50:54.046 --> 0:50:55.438
Go.

